In Neverland, the location for J.M Barrie’s Peter Pan, people don’t grow old. Rihanna feels as if she just came from Neverland because she hasn’t changed over time.



This is the first time we hear about the toxic relationship Rihanna and SZA sing about. Time may not stop RiRi, but the figure she sings to is restraining her. Successful or not, they’re putting an effort to stop her.
